menu.description: Our take on the ever-so-amazing baked brie appetizer. First, we let the brie take a spin in our pizza oven. Once it comes out oozy and toasted, we top it with a sweet peach compote and pair it with our house-made focaccia bread. Garnished with a balsamic reduction and parsley.
House wings are fried crispy, then tossed in a peaches & cream sweet habanero wing sauce. Served with a goat cheese crumble and a garnish of fresh peaches and parsley.
Fresh arugula and spinach tossed in a sweet peach white balsamic vinaigrette, topped with sliced shallots, candied pecans, crumbled goat cheese, and fresh peaches. This sweetie won't be around long!

menu.description: We start with a garlic oil base, then add dried rosemary, peppered bacon, sliced shallot, our three cheese blend, fresh peaches, and gorgonzola, then cook it to perfection. Topped with a beautiful arugula salad and finished with our Hot Honey.
Indulge in our signature beignets, topped with a sweet peach compote, a creamy custard drizzle, and a cloud of fresh whipped cream. Finished with a dusting of powdered sugar for a touch of elegance.

menu.description: We blend our house-roasted pork, roasted chiles, tomatillos, and cilantro into our chili verde. We then stack tortilla chips, our Nacho cheese blend, black bean corn salsa, chimichurri, and pico de gallo to create our top-selling appetizer

Slack's original dry rub wing. We take our signature crispy wings, toss them in a rub of orange zest, morita chilies, garlic, brown sugar, and coriander. Drizzled to finish with a spicy avocado-tomatillo sauce and a sprinkle of cilantro.

Fresh, never frozen wings marinated overnight. The wings are cooked to perfection and tossed in our spicy honey buffalo sauce, garnished with gorgonzola crumbles and cilantro. Served with blue cheese and celery sticks
House-made dough stuffed with ricotta and our three-cheese blend served oozing with marinara for dipping
We spice up the original Stuffed Sticks with roasted chipotles, jalapenos, red chili flakes, and spicy marinara for this devilish dish

Artichoke hearts and baby spinach mixed with cream cheese, sour cream, and seasonings. Topped with our three-cheese blend and baked to sizzling perfection. Garnished with roasted red peppers and served with house-made tortilla chips
Fresh basil chiffonade, seasoned grape tomatoes, and marinated mozzarella. Served over pieces of our house made focaccia drizzled with our balsamic reduction, with a little salt & pepper.
Oven-roasted whole garlic heads, paired with gorgonzola cream cheese spread, and pico de Gallo Served with three slices of our house made focaccia.

We take a toasted Stone Ground Bakery ciabatta dressed with avocado spread and roasted red pepper aioli and stack it with our house-spiced turkey, peppered bacon, and smoked provolone. Come float the river!

We take our homemade dough, bake it, and stuff it with marinated roasted chicken, romaine lettuce tossed with our caesar dressing, pico de gallo, and fresh parmesean cheese. So good it'll have you looking over your shoulder!

Toasted Stone Ground Bakery ciabatta dressed with house black bean hummus, avocado spread, Asian pickled cucumbers, tomatoes, shallots, red peppers, mixed greens, and a balsamic reduction. Veg out on this!

House-made meatballs, marinara, and smoked provolone stuffed in a Stone Ground Bakery hoagie. We serve it up with house marinara for dipping

We sear our house roasted pork, marinated in a citrus, mustard and vinegar sauce, toss on a layer of sliced ham and smoked provolone. Place that into a pressed ciabatta with chopped dill pickles, and a drizzle of creama.

Honey buffalo base to start, roasted chicken, peppered bacon, red onions, and our three cheese blend. Topped with gorgonzola crumbles, a drizzle of honey buffalo sauce, and cilantro to finish

Garlic-infused olive oil topped with shaved gyro lamb, grape tomatoes, sliced red onions, and our three-cheese blend. Finished with our tzatziki drizzle, feta, and diced cucumbers. OPA!
The Owner's favorite pizza with house marinara, pepperoni, herbed sausage, red onion, roasted red bell peppers, and our three-cheese blend
Spicy house marinara, pepperoni, roasted chipotle, red onions, roasted garlic, jalapenos, and our three-cheese blend. Topped with a drizzle of spicy marinara. The name speaks for itself
Starting smoothly with a green goddess base, we add seasoned grape tomatoes, jalapenos, and our three-cheese blend. We finish strong with fresh sliced avocado, feta, and cilantro

This Indian-inspired pie begins with Masala sauce as the base, dressed with marinated chicken, basmati rice, red onions, and our three-cheese blend. Then a drizzle of masala sauce, and a pinch of cilantro

Your choice of garlic-infused olive oil or house marinara, topped with our three-cheese blend. Add your choice of fresh gorgonzola and/or feta cheese to finish this classic

Garlic-infused olive oil base, blistered red grapes, peppered bacon, rosemary, gorgonzola crumbles, and our three-cheese blend. Finished with our house-made balsamic reduction. Sweet meets savory in this mind-bending pizza!
Garlic-infused olive oil base, herbed sausage, Kalamata olives, seasoned grape tomatoes, roasted artichoke hearts, roasted garlic, and our three cheese blend. Topped with feta

This pizza starts with garlic olive oil, then topped with sliced ham, our house-roasted pork, and our three-cheese blend then cooked to perfection. Topped with sliced pickles, a drizzle of mustard, and crema. Garnished with parsley

This adventurous pie starts with a green goddess base, seasoned shrimp, black bean corn salsa, and our three-cheese blend. Finished with our maple citrus coleslaw, pico de Gallo, and a drizzle of our house chimichurri sauce. Garnished with cilantro and lime wedge

Athletic Lite is a light brew, completely reimagined. It s classically simple but expertly crafted with 25 calories, 5 carbs, and organic grains. We brewed it specifically for the sport of life and all the good times that come with it.

Atltica is a refreshingly bright take on a Mexican-style copper. Using the finest Munich malts, it boasts a lightly toasted malt character with a whisper of spicy florals before rolling into smooth and lightly sweet waves of bread crust and wheat. A medium-body brew that is big in flavor, it s the epitome of easy drinking. A smooth and satisfying cooler must-have.

menu.item_name: Athletic Brewing Free Wave Hazy IPA
menu.description: Our Free Wave Hazy IPA is meant for the open road. Whether you re cruising the Pacific Coast Highway in a convertible or tracing your way up the coast on your bike, our Free Wave doesn t cut corners. This mouth watering IPA is loaded with Amarillo, Citra, and Mosaic hops.
The ultimate session-able IPA. Brewed with a blend of Northwest hops with Citra and Mosaic at the forefront. Body of premium organic malts from US & Germany. Subtle yet complex malt profile.

Refreshing, clean, balanced, light-bodied. Aromas subtle with floral and earthy notes. Brewed with premium organic malts from US & Germany along with combo of English and traditional American hops to the golden ale style. 50 Calories.
House lemonade with fresh muddled mint. Garnished with mint.

We founded this company with the sole mission of creating genuine craft beers, that were also non-alcoholic. Our non-alcoholic Hazy IPA is that mission in spades. Honeyed amber in color, it has a strong hop-forward aroma with hints of resinous pine and grapefruit. Its luscious medium body has a smooth, complex citrus flavor with a full and lively mouthfeel and a dry finish. Finally, a non-alcoholic craft beer for real craft beer drinkers.

The complement to the Hazy had to be easy-drinking, approachable, and low calorie, yet full of flavor and authenticity. We used a combination of Cologne and Pilsner malts and Hallertau Traditional hops to create a refreshingly complex Kolsch-style ale. Its sturdy caramel malt flavor is perfectly balanced by the citrusy hops, leaving a bright and crisp finish. The quintessential embodiment of 'ALL DAY. EVERY DAY.'

menu.item_name: Best Day Brewing West Coast IPA
menu.description: Our non-alcoholic West Coast IPA is a tribute to our back yard and its rich history of making damn good beers. Its Cascade hops are an ode to the beers that started the IPA revolution. The rich malt backbone provides ample structure for the grapefruit Cascade notes to shine. Drink up, get out there.

Also enjoy the deliciously long, dry finish.
